text: Steven T. Kuykendall (January 27, 1947 â€“ January 23, 2021) was an American Republican politician. Kuykendall was born in McAlester, Oklahoma. Kuykendall was a member of the U.S. House of Representatives from from 1999 to 2001. Kuykendall was also a member of the California State Assembly from 1994 to 1998. Kuykendall died of pulmonary fibrosis on January 23, 2021, in Long Beach, California at age 73. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official site *CNN candidate profile *Voting record maintained by The Washington Post * Category:1947 births Category:2021 deaths Category:American Presbyterians Category:United States representatives from California Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Deaths from pulmonary fibrosis Category:Politicians from Oklahoma Category:People from McAlester, Oklahoma
